data.description: Ready to escape the hustle/bustle of city living?  Bring your toys/animals, private/peaceful country living within the gated community of Deep Creek in the A+ rated school district! Nestled among a picturesque setting with nearly five acres, this exceptional custom-built modern farmhouse blends clean lines, neutral color palettes, and layered textures to create a timeless and unique look. Chef's kitchen features custom cabinetry, stainless 8 burner gas range, beautiful countertops, double oven, oversized stainless fridge and huge island with bar seating. Primary suite boasts a coffered ceiling, chandelier, breathtaking marble bathroom w/ multiple shower heads & soaking tub, separate vanities and a massive custom walk-in closet. 3 additional bedrooms downstairs including a Jack/Jill large shower and custom tilework. Upstairs is a versatile media/game room or possibly a 5th bedroom. The home is packed with custom features and upgrades including: tankless hot water heater, Trane HVAC w/4 zones, upgraded lighting, huge pantry with built-ins, lighted stairs, glass barn doors, wine cooler, extended patio, and mudroom lockers (see upgrade list for more).   Fiber internet service available. Deep Creek offers over 75 acres of nature preserve with multiple access points to the St. Mary's River so you can enjoy all the outdoors has to offer. The neighborhood also features a private lake for entertaining and cookouts.
